{
  "texts": [
    "The coarse-grained instructions without explicit constraints were set to statement level.",
    "As a result, the instructions are now divided into five granularities.",
    "Descriptions and examples of these instructions are shown in Figure 2.",
    "From the figure we can see, the coarser the granularity, the closer the instructions are to the usage habits of real users.",
    "Real users are unlikely to provide complex API names and detailed parameters like \"41.3851 • N latitude\"."
  ]
}